title: Team Treehouse - Python Courses And Workshops
description:
This is my personal collection of python material (courses and workshops) from team treehouse.


What's Inside?
==============

Courses ->

   1)Customizing Django Templates.
   2)Customizing the Django Admin.
   3)Django Forms.
   4)Django ORM.
   5)Flask REST API.

Workshops ->

   1)CSV and JSON in Python.
   2)Functional Programming With Python.
   3)Image Manipulation with Python.
   4)PyCharm.
   5)Python Comprehensions.
   6)Python Decorators.
   7)Python File IO.
   8)Setting Up a Local Python Environment (MAC).
   9)Setting Up a Local Python Environment (Windows).
  10)Tkinter.
  11)Using the Requests Library.


If there's any course/workshop/class from teamtreehouse or skillshare that you want then make a request here and I'll upload them if I have them.
